# Implementation Plan - Fix Partner Onboarding Form Link

Currently, the "Apply for Onboarding" link on the Academy gateway page is a static `mailto:` link:
`mailto:partners@karayabandhu.com?subject=Inquiry for Partner Onboarding`

Many users do not have a configured default desktop email client, making `mailto:` links appear broken or unresponsive. To provide a premium and seamless experience, we will replace this link with a fully interactive **Partner Onboarding Application Modal** directly in the landing page UI.

This modal will allow prospective service providers ("Bandhus") to apply directly, automatically saving their application to the MongoDB backend via the existing `/api/applications` endpoint under the category `"Provider Onboarding"`. The submitted applications will then be visible and manageable within the Candidate Hub (ATS) tab of the Admin Portal.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The onboarding application data will be stored under the existing `applications` collection with `category: "Provider Onboarding"`. These will show up in the Admin Portal under the **Candidate Hub (ATS)** tab. This design avoids adding extra schema complexity and allows the admin to view/delete these submissions immediately.

